com.TraderLight.DayTrader.AccountMgmt

Class AccountMgr

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.TraderLight.DayTrader.AccountMgmt.AccountMgr

  • public class AccountMgr
extends java.lang.Object
    This class has many functions: 1) is the entry point to place orders from all stock strategies; 2) keeps track of all the positions we open and close through the trading day; 3) keeps track of the cash account; 4) implements risk management
    Author:
    Mario Visco
